videos.description: JD Davison weaves through traffic to find Juwan Gary for the slam dunk for the Crimson Tide.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Davison finds Gary for the slam) 2022/01/29 ESHEET

videos.headline: Davison finds Gary for the slam

videos.description: Kendall Brown makes a nice dish to Matthew Mayer for the Baylor 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Mayer knocks down the 3-pointer

videos.description: Jahvon Quinerly makes a great effort to grab the layup as Alabama leads by 6.

videos.description: Jahvon Quinerly makes a nice bounce pass to Charles Bediako for the score inside.

videos.description: Juwan Gary goes up and denies Adam Flagler of the basket.

videos.description: Noah Gurley goes up and gets a massive block on Flo Thamba as the Crimson Tide leads by double digits.

videos.description: Jaden Shackelford finds Keon Ellis in transition for the dunk as Alabama leads Baylor by double digits.
